com.foreach.across.modules.entity.registry.properties

Interface EntityPropertyFilter

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    EntityPropertyFilter.Inclusive
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    EntityPropertyFilters.Composite, EntityPropertyFilters.Exclusive, EntityPropertyFilters.Inclusive
    Functional Interface:
    This is a functional interface and can therefore be used as the assignment target for a lambda expression or method reference.

    @FunctionalInterface
public interface EntityPropertyFilter
    Functional interface for determining which properties need to be included when fetching from a EntityPropertyRegistry. There is an accompanying utility class EntityPropertyFilters that provides most common implementations.
    See Also:
    EntityPropertyFilters, EntityPropertyComparators
